  "texts": [
    "Image features for clustering were extracted using pretrained CNN models.",
    "Coltelli et al. (2014) used various handcrafted image features and self-organizing maps (SOM) for plankton image clustering.",
    "Schmarje et al. (2021) proposed a framework for handling semi-supervised classifications of fuzzy labels due to experts having different opinions.",
    "The approach is based on overclustering to identify substructures in the fuzzy labels and a loss function to improve the overclustering.",
    "The performance surpassed the one of a state-of-the-art semi-supervised method on plankton data."
  ],
